value.name: Message
value.value:
{"editor-ab0ab6a79e53a30dc54e7248message-1":"I am a bot that can perform a trend analysis as well as provide you with citation recommendations for a single topic, combination of topics or a topic description of your choice. Besides giving you a quick overview of the results I found, I offer a separate WebUI with a more comprehensive view of analysis.

#### Quick-Commands:
To quickly start either one of the functionalities I provide, you can use the following shorthand commands:
- **!citrec topic1, topic2, "topic3 with a , inside"** -> Citation Recommendation
	- *!citrec machine learning, deep learning*
	- *!citrec Time-series based academic Trend and Downtrend detection*
- **!trends topic1, topic2, "topic3 with a , inside"** -> Trend analysis
	- *!trends blockchain*
	- *!trends p2p, network protocols*

#### Conversations:
Besides the quick commands, I support a free text conversation flow. This mode offers the option to adjust search parameters for both functionalities. These flows can be initiated with:

 - Start a new trend analysis
 - Recommend be papers to cite"}

value.name: Message
value.value: {"editor-b0684910d15bbad389769e80message-1":"Adjusting the distance from 0 to 2 changes search precision. Zero distance yields highly similar publications to your query, while a distance of 2 returns broadly varied results. Fine-tune this to balance between relevance and diversity in your search outcomes. The default value for this is 0.11. Try to adjust this value in steps of +-0.01."}
